The picture tells it all. Premium increases from 25% to 116% and deductibles remain from $4,000 to $8,000. Most families don't even incur $5,000 in medical costs in a year which means you're going to pay Obamacare premiums and then pay for your medical care out of pocket.

For example a healthy 21 year old non-smoker in Illinois currently pays $229 a month for the silver plan which has a $3,000 deductible. His rate just went up by 44% to $312 a month and he still has to pay the first $3,000 of his medical care. So he'll pay $3,744 because Obamacare requires him to by law and if he has any treatment he will pay an additional $3,000 before the insurance kicks in and starts covering some of the costs. From what I understand, Obamacare does not cover 100% of every procedure which requires co-pays and there is a separate deductible for prescriptions.

To make a long story short, this healthy young man is getting screwed by our loving government. He doesn't even get a kiss.
It's happening all over folks, the UNAFFORDABLE CARE ACT is about to become doubly UNAFFORDABLE.

We need to elect Trump and repeal and replace this sucker. The deductibles are to damned high. The bronze plan has a $6,000 deductible! I raised 2 children and never in 20 years did I incur over $5,000 medical costs where I could get a deduction on taxes. NEVER!

I tell you one thing that would go a long way to Make America Great Again would be to repeal this job killing, economy strangling, household pocketbook emptying piece of shit legislation called the Affordable Care Act aka Obamacare! (formerly known as HillaryCare)
